        "content": "Snow-Shod Farm is the Snow-Shod family's farm outside Riften — run by Vulwulf and his wife Boti. Stormcloak in sympathy, like the rest of their clan.",
        "display_name": "Snow-Shod Farm",
        "emotion": "",
